      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EXTINGUISH (3) rattled home to just miss when resuming at headquarters three weeks ago. Is sure to have come on from that and is yet to miss the frame second-up from three attempts. The 3kg claim gets her in a treat at the weights and she looks perfectly poised to go one better. FALANGHINA (2) finally delivered on the back of some eye-catching finishes last time here when launching late to score with a bit in hand. Boasts a strong record over this track and trip and gets in well with the 2kg claim. Can repeat the dose. FLAMING NAVY (1) is a speedy gelding resuming for the Doudle camp. Has built a good record to start his career and attracted firm market support throughout. Strips fitter for two jumpouts and finds a nice race to kick things off. EXTRA HOT (7) drove hard to get the verdict two back in what has proven a strong form reference. Less effective last time but was still good late. Gets in light with the 2kg claim and is one to keep in mind. HOT STRUT (5) next best.",
